headline: M·A·C Cosmetics to Launch in Sephora U.S.
summary: NEW YORK,, October 29, 2025--M·A·C Cosmetics, the #1 prestige makeup brand globally, today announced its plans to launch in select U.S. Sephora locations and at Sephora at Kohl’s in the U.S. in early 2026. This retail expansion allows M·A·C to bring its high-performance products, artistry leadership, and unwavering commitment to inclusivity to even more beauty consumers nationwide.
